episodes.text: It's one of the oldest stories in the world. You came up with an idea, rolled up your sleeves, and created a product.
And now you want to get the word out and have the whole world to start using it!
So, you’ve invited your friends, family and your investors to see what you’ve got. You’ve also put together a decent Power Point presentation.
But all of a sudden people seem bored.
Some are dashing for a door.
What if instead you had a fun and dynamic presentation. Kind of like this one.
Your audience is now engaged and everyone wants to try your product!
They may even feel like getting a little loose and breaking it down right in the conference room!
Express yourself and never run out of markers again!

shape.text: And never run out of ideas or markers
